   "body" : "Remove CRITICAL_BLOCK and TRY_CRITICAL_BLOCK, and replace them with LOCK, TRY_LOCK and IS_LOCKED. These are macros that define a local CCriticalBlock variable (a boost::interprocess::scoped_lock wrapper), which is much more C++ than the if and/or for constructions in macros.\n\nI've intentionally not touched formattng/indentation where possible, in order not to break other patches. There are several cases where simplications are possible now, though.\n",
